### Passenger rates Driver (score 5)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ratings
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rideId": "{{rideId}}",
  "score": 5,
  "comment": "Great driver, very smooth ride!"
}

###

### Driver rates Passenger (score 4)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ratings
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rideId": "{{rideId}}",
  "score": 4,
  "comment": "Polite passenger, on time."
}

###

### Duplicate rating — should return 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/ratings
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rideId": "{{rideId}}",
  "score": 3
}

###

### Rating on non-completed ride — should return 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/ratings
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rideId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "score": 5
}

###

### Get all ratings for a ride
GET {{baseUrl}}/ratings/ride/{{rideId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}

###

### Get ratings received by authenticated user
GET {{baseUrl}}/ratings/received
Authorization: Bearer {{driverToken}}

###

### Get ratings given by authenticated user
GET {{baseUrl}}/ratings/given
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}
